And for the people who are unhappy with the fact that she's not a virgin, I think we should all remember one thing: Just like there's only one first, there's also only one last person in our lives. Even if the guy isn't her first, it's just as wholesome if the author shows us that there is NO DOUBT that he'll be her last. This doujin reminds me of a visual novel called Oral Lessons With Chii-chan (https://vndb.org/v19634). If you liked this doujin, then you should definitely read that VN. The story and characters are almost the same. While Chieri has much more experience than the girl from this doujin, she's also way sweeter. The VN also does a much better job than this doujin at reassuring you that those two will be together forever. It's very easy to find it online, and it's not too long.
